024package org.opt4j.benchmarks.dtlz;
025
026import static java.lang.Math.pow;
027
028import java.util.List;
029
030import org.opt4j.benchmarks.M;
031import org.opt4j.benchmarks.N;
032
033import com.google.inject.Inject;
034
035/**
036 * The {@link DTLZ6} function.
037 * 
038 * @author lukasiewycz
039 * 
040 */
041public class DTLZ6 extends DTLZ5 {
042
043        /**
044         * Constructs a {@link DTLZ6} function.
045         * 
046         * @param m
047         *            the number of objective functions.
048         * @param n
049         *            the size of the search space (length of the x vector).
050         */
051        @Inject
052        public DTLZ6(@M int m, @N int n) {
053                super(m, n);
054        }
055
056        /*
057         * (non-Javadoc)
058         * 
059         * @see org.opt4j.benchmark.dtlz.DTLZEvaluator#g(java.util.List)
060         */
061        @Override
062        protected double g(List<Double> x) {
063                double g = 0;
064                for (double e : x) {
065                        g += pow(e, 0.1);
066
067                }
068                return g;
069        }
070
071}
